      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear you about protecting my energy but it's not just about the news. it's the fundamental problem. if the planet is effectively doomed, then every choice i make, every relationship i start, every year i live... it's just wasted effort for a future that won't exist. it feels like we're all just participating in a cruel joke. why should anyone have to suffer through the slow decay of everything just to witness the end?",
